<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Overview</h2><a id="user-content-overview" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: Overview" href="#overview"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto">Magic Box is designed as a second brain that you can put everything in, and get everything out. It aims to be a comprehensive tool for managing and retrieving information efficiently. Whether it's notes, documents, or any other type of data, Magic Box helps you organize and access it with ease.</p>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Features</h2><a id="user-content-features" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: Features" href="#features"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Data Storage</strong>: Store various types of data securely.</li>
<li><strong>Search</strong>: Powerful search capabilities to find information quickly.</li>
<li><strong>API Integration</strong>: Integrate with other services using APIs.</li>
<li><strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong>: Easy-to-use interface for managing your data.</li>
<li><strong>Extensibility</strong>: Extend functionality with plugins and extensions.</li>
</ul>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Getting Started</h2><a id="user-content-getting-started" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: Getting Started" href="#getting-started"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto">To get started with Magic Box, follow the deployment instructions below and set up the browser plugin for an enhanced experience.</p>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Deployment</h2><a id="user-content-deployment" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: Deployment" href="#deployment"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Download the <a href="/import-ai/magic-box/blob/main/compose.yaml">compose.yaml</a> file.</li>
<li>Download the <a href="/import-ai/magic-box/blob/main/.env.example">.env.example</a> file, rename it to <code>.env</code>, and configure it with your OpenAI-compatible API key.</li>
<li>Run <code>docker compose up -d</code>.</li>
<li>Open your browser and go to <a href="http://localhost:8080#/test" rel="nofollow">localhost:8080#/test</a>.</li>
</ol>

<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Mobile Support</strong>: Post from iOS and Android devices.</li>
<li><strong>File Type Support</strong>: Handle various file types including PDF, DOCX, PPT, XLSX, etc.</li>
<li><strong>RSS Support</strong>: Integrate and manage RSS feeds.</li>
<li><strong>Feed Support</strong>: Support for various types of feeds for content aggregation.</li>
<li><strong>Collaboration Tools</strong>: Enable real-time collaboration on documents and data.</li>
<li><strong>Advanced Analytics</strong>: Provide insights and analytics on stored data.</li>
<li><strong>AI Integration</strong>: Leverage AI for smarter data organization and retrieval.</li>
<li><strong>Security Enhancements</strong>: Implement advanced security features to protect user data.</li>
<li><strong>Cross-Platform Sync</strong>: Ensure seamless data synchronization across multiple devices and platforms.</li>
<li><strong>Customizable Dashboards</strong>: Allow users to create and customize their own dashboards for better data visualization.</li>
<li><strong>Automated Backups</strong>: Implement automated backup solutions to prevent data loss.</li>
<li><strong>Localization</strong>: Support multiple languages for a global user base.</li>
<li><strong>User Permissions</strong>: Fine-grained user permissions and access control.</li>
<li><strong>Notification System</strong>: Implement a notification system for updates and alerts.</li>
</ul>
